modelIdentification.name: AFMSTT-ACM
modelIdentification.purpose: Defines structures for Air Control Measures
modelIdentification.description: Implements USMTF Air Control Order (ACO) routes and air spaces in a form that is optimized for HLA communications.
modelIdentification.useHistory: 1.1v2 Correct issues found during ACM implementation. Start/stop time need to be moved from ACM to APeriod. Support multiple usages per airspace shape. Control points need a minimum and maximum altitude.
1.1v3 - Remove Lat/Long DDM dimensions from all AirspaceControlMeans.
modelIdentification.other: Sean Reilly deleted federation switches table Jake Borah changed the defintion of the Fixed Record "ControlPoint" field "Altitude" to "Height in feet above mean sea level."

attribute.name: ACOIdentifier
attribute.semantics: Unique identifier of the ACO

attribute.name: ACMType
attribute.semantics: Function of the airpace. Equivalent to FIELD 1 OF SET ACMID (TYPE OF AIRSPACE CONTROL MEANS)

attribute.name: ACMIdentifier
attribute.semantics: Unique ID of the ACM

attribute.name: Force
attribute.semantics: Set the forceIdentifier for this update. * Description from the FOM: The identification of the force that the aggregate belongs to. Aggregates shall not group opposing forces together. * Description of the data type from the FOM: Enumeration distinguishing different teams or sides.

attribute.name: ACMUsage
attribute.semantics: Function of the Graphic. Equivalent to FIELD 4 OF SET ACMID (AIRSPACE USAGE) in ACO.

attribute.name: MinAltitudeType
attribute.semantics: What is the minimum altitude level this airspace involved.

attribute.name: MinAltitude
attribute.semantics: The acutal minimum altitude

attribute.name: MaxAltitudeType
attribute.semantics: What is the maximum altitude level this airspace involved.

attribute.name: MaxAltitude
attribute.semantics: The acual Max Altitude for this airspace

attribute.name: Speed
attribute.semantics: The speed in knots designated for this airspace.

attribute.name: Active
attribute.semantics: Is this airspace currently in effect or active.

attribute.name: ControlPoints
attribute.semantics: A list of all the control points that make up this airspace.

attribute.name: APeriod
attribute.semantics: Defines a time period for this air space or route.

objectClass.name: Line
objectClass.semantics: An array of lat/long positions (LLPosition) that make of the shape of this airspace

attribute.name: Positions
attribute.semantics: Required Attribute. A collection of LLposition objects that make of the airspace

objectClass.name: Corridor
objectClass.semantics: Data that defines the airspace corridor

attribute.name: Width
attribute.semantics: Required: The Width of the Airspace Corridor

attribute.name: Positions
attribute.semantics: Required: Positions that define the airspace corridor

objectClass.name: Polyarc
objectClass.semantics: Data that defines a Polyarc Airspace

attribute.name: Origin
attribute.semantics: Required: The center of the Polyarc Airspace

attribute.name: BeginRadialBearing
attribute.semantics: Required: The relationship of the start bearing from the origin/center

attribute.name: Radius
attribute.semantics: Required: The radius of the polyarc

attribute.name: EndRadialBearning
attribute.semantics: Required: The relationship of the end bearing from the origin/center

attribute.name: Positions
attribute.semantics: Required: The set of positions that define the polyarc

objectClass.name: Radarc
objectClass.semantics: Set of data that defines a Radarc

attribute.name: Origin
attribute.semantics: Required: Origin of the Radarc

attribute.name: StartRadialBearing
attribute.semantics: Required: The bearing (0<=360) where the arc begins

attribute.name: EndRadialBearing
attribute.semantics: Required: The bearing (0<=360) where the arc ends

attribute.name: InnerRadius
attribute.semantics: Required: Inner radius of the arc

attribute.name: OuterRadius
attribute.semantics: Required: Outer radius of the arc

objectClass.name: Polygon
objectClass.semantics: Data that defines the polygon airspace

attribute.name: Positions
attribute.semantics: Required: Set of positions that define the Polygon Airspace

objectClass.name: Circle
objectClass.semantics: Set of data defining the circle airspace

attribute.name: Center
attribute.semantics: Required: The center of the circle airspace

attribute.name: Radius
attribute.semantics: Required: The radius of the cirlce airspace

objectClass.name: Track
objectClass.semantics: Set of data that defines a Track airspace

attribute.name: BeginPoints
attribute.semantics: Required: Set of points that define the beginning of a Track Airspace

attribute.name: EndPoints
attribute.semantics: Required: Set of Points that define the end of track airspace

attribute.name: LeftWidths
attribute.semantics: Required: Set of doubles that represent the Left Width of the Track Airspace

attribute.name: RightWidths
attribute.semantics: Required: Set of doubles that represent the Left Width of the Track Airspace

attribute.name: MinAltitudeTypes
attribute.semantics: type of altitudes contrained in the MinAltitudes array

attribute.name: MinAltitude_Array
attribute.semantics: Set of altitudes that define the Track altitude

attribute.name: MaxAltitudeTypes
attribute.semantics: type of altitudes contrained in the MaxAltitudes array

attribute.name: MaxAltitude_Array
attribute.semantics: Set of maximum altitudes for a Track Airspace

objectClass.name: Point
objectClass.semantics: Set of data for a point airspace

attribute.name: Position
attribute.semantics: Required: Position of the Point Airspace

objectClass.name: Orbit
objectClass.semantics: Set of data that defines an Orbit Airspace

attribute.name: FirstPoint
attribute.semantics: Required: The first point in the orbit airspace

attribute.name: SecondPoint
attribute.semantics: Required: The second point in the orbit airspace

attribute.name: Width
attribute.semantics: Required: The width of the Orbit Airspace

attribute.name: Alignment
attribute.semantics: The Alignment of the orbit

enumeratedData.name: AltitudeTypeEnum
enumeratedData.semantics: Altitude Types: BR_GL == Base Reference, Ground Level BR_MSL == Base Reference,Mean Sea Level RA_AGL == Relative Altitude, Above Ground Level RA_AMSL == Relative Altitude, Above Mean Sea Level FL == Flight Level

enumeratedData.name: ControlPointTypeEnum
enumeratedData.semantics: Types of control points supported USMTF definitions

enumeratedData.name: GraphicFunctionEnum
enumeratedData.semantics: Function of the airpace. Equivalent to FIELD 1 OF SET ACMID (TYPE OF AIRSPACE CONTROL MEANS).

enumeratedData.name: GraphicUsageEnum
enumeratedData.semantics: Function of the graphic. Equivalent to FIELD 4 OF SET ACMID (AIRSPACE USAGE) in ACO.

enumeratedData.name: AlignmentEnum
enumeratedData.semantics: Relative location of the track relative to the route.

arrayData.name: ControlPoint_Array
arrayData.semantics: Point that define the size,shape (area) of air space.

arrayData.name: APeriodArray
arrayData.semantics: Defines a list of time periods for an air space or route.

arrayData.name: GraphicUsageArray
arrayData.semantics: List of function for each graphic. Equivalent to FIELD 4 OF SET ACMID (AIRSPACE USAGE) in ACO.

fixedRecordData.name: ControlPoint
fixedRecordData.semantics: Detailed information on the specific control point.

field.name: MinAltitudeType
field.semantics: Determines the unit of measurement for the associated altitude attribute.

field.name: MaxAltitudeType
field.semantics: Determines the unit of measurement for the associated altitude attribute.

fixedRecordData.name: APeriodStruct
fixedRecordData.semantics: Defines a time period for an air space or route.

field.name: StartTime
field.semantics: The time this airspace is in effect (active)

field.name: StopTime
